Metadata: Senate Tribute to Dr. Edward C. Monahan
Congressional Record, Proceedings and Debates of the 116th Congress, First Session, Washington DC, Volume 165, No. 168, October 23, 2019
Article was spawned from a symposium where Dr. Edward C. Monahan was honored on July 26, 2019; talks given by Sylvain De Guise and Nancy Balcom from the Connecticut Sea Grant Program
Tribute by Senator Richard Blumenthal of former Connecticut Sea Grant Director Dr. Edward C. Monahan.
